OL,3,CNew NHS GP walk-in clinic set to open
OL,4,Cin Stranraer and Hawick
OL,6,FTwo new NHS GP walk-in clinics are set
OL,7,Fto open in the south of Scotland this
OL,8,Fyear in an announcement by the First
OL,9,FMinister.
OL,11,FJohn Swinney has said that Stranraer
OL,12,Fand Hawick will both benefit from the
OL,13,Fnew NHS services which will allow
OL,14,Fpeople to access GP-led care without
OL,15,Fan appointment.
OL,17,FThe walk-in centre in Stranraer is set
OL,18,Fto open on Tuesday 14 April 2026 with
OL,19,Fthe one in Hawick set to open sometime
OL,20,Fin April.
