PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1771952662
OL,3,CNew NHS GP walk-in clinic set to open
OL,4,Cin Stranraer and Hawick
OL,6,FThe Scottish Government say the walk-
OL,7,Fins will complement traditional GP
OL,8,Fservices and urgent care.
OL,10,FIn a statement, First Minister John
OL,11,FSwinney said: "I committed to
OL,12,Fdelivering 15 new walk-in GP centres
OL,13,Fand I am pleased that, not only will
OL,14,Fwe now deliver an initial 16 sites,
OL,15,Fbut many of these will be up and
OL,16,Frunning in a matter of weeks.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
