OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1771952662
OL,3,CNew NHS GP walk-in clinic set to open
OL,4,Cin Stranraer and Hawick
OL,6,F"With centres open 12-8pm, seven days
OL,7,Fa week, and based in easily accessible
OL,8,Flocations in our communities across
OL,9,Fthe country, this is part of a package
OL,10,Faddressing the 8am rush that has
OL,11,Ffrustrated so many of us - easing
OL,12,Fcapacity pressures on family doctors.
OL,14,F"By establishing a series of walk-in
OL,15,Fclinics we can ensure people are seen
OL,16,Fby a clinician at a time that works
OL,17,Ffor them. Our programme will help us
OL,18,Fdeliver over one million additional GP
OL,19,Fand nurse appointments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
