PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1771952662
OL,3,CNew NHS GP walk-in clinic set to open
OL,4,Cin Stranraer and Hawick
OL,6,F"This complements our #531 million
OL,7,Flandmark investment in core general
OL,8,Fpractice. With GP numbers up, long
OL,9,Fwaits down and new walk-in GP clinics
OL,10,Fbeing tested across Scotland, it is
OL,11,Fclear we are making real progress in
OL,12,Four NHS and I am determined to
OL,13,Fcontinue driving forward improvements."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/4
